org.biopax.validator.utils

Class BiopaxOntologyManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.biopax.psidev.ontology_manager.impl.OntologyManagerImpl
      • org.biopax.validator.utils.BiopaxOntologyManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OntologyManager, CvValidator

    public class BiopaxOntologyManager
extends OntologyManagerImpl
implements CvValidator
    Access to BioPAX controlled vocabularies. This component is built from a modified PSIDEV tool, OntologyAccess Manager, by extending it and adding several "proxy" methods that allow to extract validator-specific data only once and free the memory after it, if required. However, it does not hide base class's methods. REQUIRES INTERNET CONNECTION (when configured to use OBO URLs)
    Author:
    rodche
